title: Ep 49: Your Worst Fears and Halloween!
description: This episode I asked you the listeners to write in with your biggest fears in life. I read your emails and discuss some of mine as well. What can we do to not be reduced to terrified little guppies by our fears? Also, why the Misfits are awesome and ridiculous at the same time.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
